<div class="content">
<p>My new <a href="../2002/html2text.1">html2text Converter</a> (<a href="../2002/html2text.py">Python source</a>) will convert any HTML web page into <a href="../2002/html2text?url=http:%252F%252Fwww.aaronsw.com%252Fweblog%252F">gloriously plain ASCII text</a>.<form action="../2002/html2text.1" method="GET"></p>

<p><strong>URI:</strong> <input type="text" name="url" /> <input type="submit" value="Go" /></p>

<p>Well, enjoy. Comments and patches appreciated as usual.</form></p>

